@Access_Token = 在这里粘贴通过 OIDC 获取的 access_token
@Gateway_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000
@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5100

### WeatherForecast
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v2/WeatherForecast/Get
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取全部用户
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetUserList
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 查询指定用户
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetUserById/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 关注用户
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UserFollow/Follow
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "targetUserId": 20002
}

### 获取关注状态
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UserFollow/GetFollowStatus?targetUserId=20002
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取我的粉丝列表
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UserFollow/GetMyFollowers?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取我的关注列表
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UserFollow/GetMyFollowing?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取我的关系链动态流
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UserFollow/GetMyFollowingFeed?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 取消关注用户
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/UserFollow/Unfollow
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "targetUserId": 20002
}

### 获取登录用户的租户下全部业务数据-字段隔离
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Tenant/BusinessTable
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取登录用户的租户下全部业务数据-表隔离
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Tenant/MultiBusinessTable
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取登录用户的租户下全部业务数据-库隔离
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Tenant/SubLibBusinessTable
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 使用缓存获取全部租户列表
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Tenant/GetTenantWithCache
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 测试添加一个租户
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Tenant/AddTest
Accept: application/json
Authorization:Bearer {{Access_Token}}

